OL,3,CPeople asked not to go to Bristol
OL,4,Chospital as critical incident declared
OL,6,FInterim chief medical officer at UHBW
OL,7,FDr Rebecca Maxwell said: "We have
OL,8,Fdeclared a critical incident due to a
OL,9,Fpower outage. We aim to have this
OL,10,Ffully resolved as soon as possible.
OL,12,F"All patients, visitors and colleagues
OL,13,Fare safe.
OL,15,F"We ask the public not to attend our
OL,16,FBristol city centre hospitals until
OL,17,Fthe incident is resolved and use
OL,18,Falternative services in the area.
OL,20,F"We thank you for your cooperation."
